  "texts": [
    "To the best of our knowledge, this paper is the first comprehensive review of the interplay between xenophobia and AI.",
    "In total we look at its impact across five domains: social media, healthcare, immigration, employment, as well as via large pre-trained models.",
    "We proceed as follows.",
    "First, in Sect. 2, we define xenophobia, distinguishing it from other forms of discriminatory attitudes and practices such as racism and sexism, and specifying its conceptual relevance to AI systems.",
    "We then, in Sect. 3 discuss how xenophobia may manifest across a number of AI application domains."
  ],
